<section class="thankyou-section" aria-labelledby="thankyou-heading">
  <div class="thankyou-hero">
    <img src="/images/icons/party-popper.svg" alt="" class="thankyou-icon" aria-hidden="true">
    <h1 id="thankyou-heading">Thank You for Taking Action!</h1>
    <p class="section-intro">
      You've taken an important step in advocating for senior living. Your invitation can lead
      to a meaningful visit that shapes how your lawmaker understands the needs of older
      Americans and the professionals who serve them.
    </p>
  </div>

  <section class="next-steps" aria-labelledby="next-heading">
    <h2 id="next-heading">What Happens Next</h2>
    <ol class="next-steps-list">
      <li>
        <strong>Follow up in 5-7 business days</strong> if you haven't heard back.
        A quick phone call to the scheduler's office is the most effective follow-up.
        <br>
        <a href="/api/calendar-reminder" class="btn btn-outline calendar-btn" download>
          Add Follow-Up Reminder to Calendar
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Prepare for the visit.</strong> Review the resources below,
        identify key residents and staff members the lawmaker
        should meet, and prepare talking points on issues that matter to your community.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Take photos!</strong> With permission, capture photos of the visit to share with
        Argentum and on social media (tag <strong>@argentum</strong>).
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Send a thank-you note</strong> to the lawmaker's office after the visit using
        the template below.
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="prep-section" aria-labelledby="prep-heading">
    <h2 id="prep-heading">Resource Center</h2>
    <p>
      A successful visit starts with good preparation. Review these resources to help frame
      your conversations with lawmakers and strengthen your advocacy.
    </p>
    <div class="prep-cards-grid">
      <div class="prep-card">
        <div class="prep-card-inner">
          <img src="/images/icons/page-document.svg" alt="" class="prep-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="prep-info">
            <h3>Value of Assisted Living &mdash; Argentum Solutions 2026</h3>
            <p>
              Key facts and figures about the senior living industry. Covers workforce,
              resident care, economic impact, and policy priorities.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="prep-actions">
          <a href="/documents/value-of-assisted-living-2026.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
             class="btn btn-primary">
            View &amp; Download Infographic (PDF)
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prep-card">
        <div class="prep-card-inner">
          <img src="/images/icons/globe.svg" alt="" class="prep-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="prep-info">
            <h3>Standing With Seniors &mdash; Interactive Map &amp; Advocacy Hub</h3>
            <p>
              Explore Argentum's advocacy platform with an interactive map showing
              senior living's impact in your state.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="prep-actions">
          <a href="https://www.argentum.org/advocacy/standing-with-seniors/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
             class="btn btn-primary">
            Explore Standing With Seniors
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="prep-tips">
      <h3>How to Use These Resources</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Before the visit:</strong> Review the key statistics so you can weave them into your conversation naturally.</li>
        <li><strong>During the visit:</strong> Print the infographic to hand to the lawmaker or their staff&mdash;it serves as a professional leave-behind.</li>
        <li><strong>After the visit:</strong> Reference specific data points in your thank-you follow-up to reinforce your message.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="followup-letter" aria-labelledby="followup-heading">
    <h2 id="followup-heading">Post-Visit Thank You Letter</h2>
    <p>After the tour, send this follow-up letter to the lawmaker's office. Customize the bracketed fields with details from your visit.</p>

    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="followup-body">Thank You / Follow-Up Letter</label>
      <textarea id="followup-body" rows="20" readonly><%= followupLetter %></textarea>
    </div>

    <div class="letter-actions">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary copy-followup-btn" id="copy-followup">
        Copy Follow-Up Letter
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="share-section" aria-labelledby="share-heading">
    <h2 id="share-heading">Share With Argentum</h2>
    <div class="share-card">
      <p>
        <strong>Please send photos and a brief summary of your visit</strong> to Argentum's
        policy team so we can amplify your advocacy work!
      </p>
      <div class="share-contact">
        <p>
          <strong>Kyle Loeber</strong><br>
          Senior Manager, Public Policy &amp; Advocacy<br>
          <a href="mailto:kloeber@argentum.org">kloeber@argentum.org</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="share-note">
        Have questions at any point in this process? Don't hesitate to reach out to Kyle at the
        email above. We're here to support your advocacy efforts.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-actions">
    <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Invite Another Lawmaker</a>
  </div>
</section>
